experimental design: This experiment compares spliceosome positioning in LU99 cells plus and minus PRMT5 inhibition, by using iCLIP with antibodies against SmB. Control samples were treated with DMSO for either 24 or 48hrs and test samples were treated with 500nM GSK-595 or 100nM LLY-283 PRMT5 inhibitors for 24 or 48 hours. A Non-crosslinked sample were also prepared using cells treated with DMSO for 48 hours. RNase treatments = 0.8 units/ml.
